HEADWORD: Ehlite
<hw>Eh"lite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From <ets>Ehl</ets>
near Linz, where it occurs.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>A mineral of a
